gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 108, Spurs 98
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Spurs 108-98, as they moved to 25-23 on the year. Paolo Banchero led the Magic with 25 points, nine rebounds, and seven assists as Franz Wagner added 20 points, 8 rebounds, and five assists. Devin Vassell (26 points, four rebounds, four assists) and Jeremy Sochan (18 points, 12 rebounds) led the Spurs as Victor Wembanyama added 21 points, eight rebounds, and six blocks.
